{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have you ever strolled through your local mall and thought to yourself: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u201cI could totally build something like this myself!\u201d</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Well, now you can!</strong> Mall Craze is a Shopping Center Management game where you become the architect and owner of your very own mall! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/Build_New_Optimized.gif?t=1737972661\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Your Dream Mall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you want to replicate your favorite real-world shopping center or let your imagination run wild with a unique design, ultimately, the choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from an array of shops and create a mall that stands out from the rest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/MallCrazeDividerBuild.png?t=1737972661\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/Customize_New_Optimized.gif?t=1737972661\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize Every Detail</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who says all malls have to look the same? <br>With Mall Craze, you have the power to personalize every aspect of your mall. <br>Want a sleek, modern design? No problem. Prefer a cozy, rustic vibe?  <br>The options are there for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/MallCrazeDividerCustomize.png?t=1737972661\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/Manage_New_Optimized.gif?t=1737972661\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become the Manager</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once your mall is built, it's time to put on your managerial hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire experienced cashiers <i>(or make tough decisions and let underperforming employees go)</i>, launch strategic advertising campaigns, secure financing through bank loans, and fine-tune your pricing strategy to maximize profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With smart decisions, your mall will financially thrive in no time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/MallCrazeDividerManage.png?t=1737972661\" /><i>Curious to see how far your architectorial, creative &amp; managerial talents can take you?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/MallCrazeStaffBottom.png?t=1737972661\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737972661","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/page.bg.jpg?t=1737972661","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737972661","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737972661","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2250920,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have you ever strolled through your local mall and thought to yourself: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u201cI could totally build something like this myself!\u201d</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Well, now you can!</strong> Mall Craze is a Shopping Center Management game where you become the architect and owner of your very own mall! </p><p class=\"bb_p